> \cin{The word EOF must be at the beginning of the line.}
> \cin{EOF}   \mycomment{บอก\wbr{}จบ\wbr{}ข้อ\wbr{}มูล\wbr{}นำ\wbr{}เข้า}
$ \cin{cat file.txt}
