--More--\cursorprompt \myleftarrow \thtt{กด} \ovalbox{\cmd{q}} \thtt{เพื่อ\wbr{}ยก\wbr{}เลิก\wbr{}การ\wbr{}แดง\wbr{}ผล}
$ \textcolor{blue}{x}
$ \textcolor{blue}{xd}\cursorprompt\ovalbox{\cmd{Tab}}\ovalbox{\cmd{Tab}}
xdelta         xditview       xdpyinfo       xdvi.bin
